releaseNotes:
0.3.0 - introduced IInteractionOption, which derives from IInteraction, Extracted IInteraction.IsRunEnabled into IInteractionOption.IsRunEnabled
      0.2.0 - IInteraction now supports querying if the Interaction may be run
      0.1.1 - IInteractionExtensions.TryRunAsync Extension now passes parameter initialValue to RunAsync of extended IInteraction
      0.1.0 - initial release
